  nwourms@netscape.net (Nicholas Wourms) closes bug 6111.

  15 Aug 2002; Dan Armak <danarmak@gentoo.org> ChangeLog  :

  Fix compilation - wrong path to makefile was being specified. Fixes
  bug #6023.

